<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-part" ?><part xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_3aaf1df9-dc92-448e-86ee-c469d1fe194e" outputclass="ncc-part"><num>J5</num><title id="_d6c79631-3d76-4b2f-9212-0fc84f1a33a0">Building sealing</title><part-variation deleted-text="For a Class 2 building and Class 4 part of a building, Section J is replaced with Section J of BCA 2009 (without NT variation). For Class 3 and Class 5-9 buildings, Section J of NCC 2025 does not apply and from is replaced with Section J of NCC 2019 (without NT variation)." variation="NT" variation-type="DELETE">NT DELETE Part</part-variation><intro-part id="_56a96e4e-1d9d-44c4-8ffc-014f58fa8a7d"><p>This Part contains <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_a8928c55-630a-41ee-8e81-b8015025bb27" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> for compliance with Part J1. It sets out provisions for sealing a building to prevent air leakage. The provisions are intended to improve occupant thermal comfort by increasing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1259_5.7.0.xml#_71ea06f9-79ec-4eae-bdf4-d90302f51eb5" id="_d36884d0-f1de-4ddc-8161-49cf57251fd2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">envelope</xref> efficacy and reduce the energy consumption of any installed <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_067cf52e-cd4e-4a06-8005-909509fd942c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> systems.</p></intro-part><subtopic id="_6fdd8c8c-13f0-4a84-b363-45630b466706" subtopic-type="provision"><clauseref id="_428bba53-87d8-4172-8c5b-21